  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Solution Architect (Government Digital Solutions)",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking an experienced Solution Architect to lead the design and delivery of enterprise-grade digital solutions for Whole-of-Government (WOG) customers. This role focuses on architecting secure, scalable, and reusable platforms aligned with Singapore’s digital government frameworks, supporting large-scale digital transformation initiatives.</p><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><p><ul><li>Lead end-to-end solution architecture for enterprise digital applications, workflows, portals, and data platforms.</li><li>Design modular, scalable architectures aligned with government frameworks and security standards.</li><li>Define technical strategies, roadmaps, and architecture standards with business unit leadership.</li><li>Collaborate with enterprise software vendors to design and integrate platform solutions.</li><li>Provide architectural oversight for complex, multi-agency system implementations.</li><li>Act as a trusted technical advisor to senior government stakeholders.</li><li>Support solution delivery, technical escalations, deployment, and handover to operations.</li></ul></p><h3>Requirements</h3><p><ul><li>10+ years of experience in solution architecture, enterprise systems delivery, or public-sector digital transformation.</li><li>Strong experience with enterprise application platforms and complex systems integration.</li><li>Proven experience working with enterprise software OEMs.</li><li>Deep understanding of government frameworks, cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP), security standards, and enterprise integration.</li><li>Experience with AI-enabled solutions, cloud-based platforms, and digital transformation initiatives is a plus.</li><li>Familiarity with Agile and DevSecOps practices; certifications such as Scrum Master, SAFe, or PMP are preferred.</li><li>Strong stakeholder engagement, leadership, and communication skills.</li></ul></p><p><br /><strong>To Apply</strong><br />To apply or find out more information on this role, please email us or send in your updated resume to:<br /><a href=\"https://www.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/job/information-technology/cloud-security-engineer-star-career-consulting-ab89cb320ecde87bec0a37286f341b44#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">lynn.tay@starcareerconsulting.com</a></p><p><strong>Lynn Tay</strong> (Reg. No. R1876711)<br /><strong>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD</strong> (EA Licence: 20C0353)</p>",
